# MIROLYUBOV ILYA VODOROD TEST TASK

Installing and activating virtual environment:

    python -m venv venv
    source venv/bin/activate

Deactivating:

    deactivate

Installing dependencies:

    pip install -r requirements.txt

Creating .env file:

    DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:12345@localhost:5432/server_db
    ALEMBIC_URL=postgresql://postgres@localhost:5432/server_db

    HOST=localhost
    PORT=8000

    NBRB_API_URL=https://api.nbrb.by/exrates/rates


## Database Migrations

    alembic upgrade head

## Runing

    uvicorn app.app:app --reload

<hr>

## Runing with docker

    docker-compose -f docker-compose up

